YouTube bụ nkekọrịta vidiyo n'ịntanetị nke America na usoro mgbasa ozi mmekọrịta nke nwere isi na San Bruno, California
Ọ malitere na Febụwarị 14, 2005, site n'aka Steve Chen, Chad Hurley, na Jawed Karim
Ọ bụ Google nwe ya, ọ bụkwa ebe nrụọrụ weebụ nke abụọ a na-eleta, mgbe Google Search gasịrị

YouTube nwere ihe karịrị ijeri 2.5 ndị ọrụ kwa ọnwa na-ele ihe karịrị otu ijeri awa vidiyo kwa ụbọchị. As of May 2019[update] 2019[update], a na-ebugo vidiyo na ọnụego nke ihe karịrị awa 500 nke ọdịnaya kwa nkeji.YouTube enweela mmetụta mmekọrịta ọha na eze na-enwetụbeghị ụdị ya, na-emetụta omenala ndị a ma ama, usoro ịntanetị, na ịmepụta ndị ama ama multimillionaire
N'agbanyeghị uto na ihe ịga nke ọma ya, YouTube katọrọ ọtụtụ ebe
Nkatọ YouTube gụnyere webụsaịtị a na-eji mee ka mgbasa ozi na-ezighi ezi, okwu nwebisiinka, imebi nzuzo nke ndị ọrụ ya, na-eme ka nyocha, na itinye nchekwa na ọdịmma ụmụaka n'ihe egwu.
